  "text": "During these experiments, we measured the hydration energies for reaction 5 to support the validity of the present results and provide bases for comparison with the data obtained in previous studies. Table 1 shows that the values measured in this work are in good agreement with those measured previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
